videos.description: Danny Green throws up a lob pass to a streaking LaMarcus Aldridge in transition, who finishes the play with an emphatic alley-oop dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Green lobs it to Aldridge for big slam) 2016/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Green lobs it to Aldridge for big slam

videos.description: LaMarcus Aldridge could not miss in the first quarter, shooting 9-for-9 from the quarter and scoring 20 points against the Bulls.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Aldridge flawless in first quarter going 9-9) 2016/12/25 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Aldridge flawless in first quarter going 9-9 in Spurs' win

videos.description: Jimmy Butler finds a wide-open lane to the basket where he receives a pass from Taj Gibson and jams home a two-handed dunk against the Spurs.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler cuts backdoor for open slam) 2016/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler cuts backdoor for open slam

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard races to the basket to grab the rebound off David Lee's missed shot and throws down a two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Leonard cleans up missed shot with putback dunk) 2016/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Leonard cleans up missed shot with putback dunk

videos.description: Patty Mills lobs up an alley-oop pass for Dewayne Dedmon who throws down a thunderous two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dedmon exhilarates Spurs with alley-oop jam) 2016/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dedmon exhilarates Spurs with alley-oop jam

videos.description: As a courtesy to Gregg Popovich on Christmas day, Israel Gutierrez only asks the Spurs coach one question before letting him go back to the bench.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Gutierrez present to Popovich: A short interview) 2016/12/25

videos.headline: Gutierrez present to Popovich: A short interview

videos.description: Up by seven points in the fourth quarter, Danny Green knocks down two 3-pointers to give the Spurs a double-digit lead over the Bulls.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Green extends lead with back-to-back 3-pointers in win) 2016/12/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Green extends lead with back-to-back 3-pointers in win

videos.description: LaMarcus Aldridge shares how he was able to hit his first 11 shots of the game, how the team was able to maintain their play after surrendering a big lead in their victory over the Bulls and what the potential can be for the Spurs moving forward.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Aldridge: 'Anything is possible' for the Spurs) 2016/12/25

videos.headline: Aldridge: 'Anything is possible' for the Spurs
